    "# How Fare is Affected by Flight Distance"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f226c092-6a50-4371-a112-43007e8b5641",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**Cleaning data for fare by distance**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 36,
   "id": "2e1d64ba-d3a2-479f-8912-d76670565d23",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/html": [
